{
  "texts": [
    "We included both proprietary and open-weight models in our evaluation.",
    "For proprietary models, we tested OpenAI's GPT-4o-2024-05-13 47 and GPT-3.5-turbo-0125 48.",
    "For open-weight models, we selected the most popular foundational models from the HuggingFace trending text generation model list as of June 2024, including Mixtral-8x7B-v0.1 49, Mistral-7B-v0.1 50, Yi-1.5-9B, Yi-1.5-34B 51, Meta-Llama-3-8B, Meta-Llama-3-70B 52, Qwen2-7B, and Qwen2-72B 53.",
    "In addition, we evaluated two medical models based on Mistral-7B-v0.1, namely meerkat-7b-v1.0 54 and internistai/base-7b-v0.2 55, to determine if additional medical training enhances metacognitive abilities.",
    "All models were evaluated with a temperature setting of 0 to ensure reliability and reproducibility of results 56."
  ]
}